<h3 class="sectionedit15" id="openwrt_wiki_survey">OpenWrt Wiki survey</h3>
<div class="level3">
<ul>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> How often do you visit the OpenWrt Wiki?</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> What do you miss in the OpenWrt Wiki?</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> How would you rate the wiki device page of the device you own?</div>
<ul>
<li class="level2"><div class="li"> scale 1…5</div>
</li>
<li class="level2"><div class="li"> 1 = no content / bad structure / old data</div>
</li>
<li class="level2"><div class="li"> 5 = every imaginable information is available / good structure / up to date data</div>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>

</div>

